OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772561167
OL,3,CGovernment considering sending British
OL,4,Cwarship HMS Duncan to Middle East
OL,6,FThe UK government is considering
OL,7,Fsending a British warship to the
OL,8,Feastern Mediterranean to help defend
OL,9,Fthe region after a series of drone
OL,10,Fattacks on a British base in Cyprus
OL,11,Fheightened tensions in the region.
OL,13,FITV News understands that no formal
OL,14,Fdecision has yet been taken but
OL,15,Fdiscussions within government have
OL,16,Fintensified over the past 24 hours
OL,17,Fabout deploying HMS Duncan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
