FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772561167
OL,3,CGovernment considering sending British
OL,4,Cwarship HMS Duncan to Middle East
OL,6,FThe Type 45 destroyer, which
OL,7,Fspecialises in air defence, is said to
OL,8,Fbe under active consideration as the
OL,9,Fgovernment continues to assess the
OL,10,Fevolving security situation.
OL,12,FThe move follows multiple drone
OL,13,Fattacks targeting RAF Akrotiri, the
OL,14,FBritish airbase in Cyprus. The first
OL,15,Fdrone struck the runway in the early
OL,16,Fhours of yesterday morning, managing
OL,17,Fto penetrate defences. We have been
OL,18,Ftold it caused minimal damage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772561167
OL,3,CGovernment considering sending British
OL,4,Cwarship HMS Duncan to Middle East
OL,6,FTwo further drones were launched at
OL,7,Fthe base during the day but were
OL,8,Fsuccessfully intercepted before
OL,9,Freaching their target.
OL,11,FIran has claimed that they believe the
OL,12,FUnited States has relocated aircraft
OL,13,Fto Cyprus and has threatened to launch
OL,14,Fadditional missile strikes against the
OL,15,Fisland as a result.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772561167
OL,3,CGovernment considering sending British
OL,4,Cwarship HMS Duncan to Middle East
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer had said
OL,7,Fthat UK bases could be used by the
OL,8,FUnited States for "defensive" strikes
OL,9,Fagainst Iran if necessary, but
OL,10,Fgovernment sources have told ITV News
OL,11,Fthat they believe the initial drone
OL,12,Fattack was launched before that
OL,13,Fstatement was made.
OL,15,FSir Keir has also stressed that
OL,16,FBritain's bases in Cyprus are not
OL,17,Fbeing used by US bombers.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
