OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772561167
OL,3,CGovernment considering sending British
OL,4,Cwarship HMS Duncan to Middle East
OL,6,FThe deteriorating security environment
OL,7,Fhas prompted responses from other
OL,8,FEuropean allies. France has said it is
OL,9,Fplanning to send anti-missile and anti-
OL,10,Fdrone systems to Cyprus, along with a
OL,11,Ffrigate, according to the semi-
OL,12,Fofficial Cyprus News Agency.
OL,14,FGreece has also moved swiftly,
OL,15,Fconfirming it will deploy two frigates
OL,16,Fand a pair of F-16 fighter jets to the
OL,17,Fregion with immediate effect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772561167
OL,3,CGovernment considering sending British
OL,4,Cwarship HMS Duncan to Middle East
OL,6,FThe potential deployment of HMS Duncan
OL,7,Fwould signal strong British support
OL,8,Ffor Cyprus and reinforce efforts to
OL,9,Fprotect the UK's overseas bases. The
OL,10,FType 45 destroyer is equipped with
OL,11,Fsophisticated radar and missile
OL,12,Fsystems capable of intercepting
OL,13,Fdrones, aircraft and other complex
OL,14,Faerial threats.
OL,16,FDiscussions are ongoing, and we are
OL,17,Ftold no final decision has been taken.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
